    <mxCell id="e-registry" value="&lt;b&gt;Provider Registry *&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;i style=&apos;font-size:10px&apos;&gt;Reclaim cloud API&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1" tooltip="* THE REAL OPERATIONAL HEADACHE: When ADP redesigns their pay statements page, changes URL structure, or renames response fields, the regex in this provider template breaks silently. No error reaches the apartment site. A Reclaim developer or community contributor must detect the change, update the provider template, and redeploy — before all existing integrations stop producing valid proofs.">
